channel.title: My new account
channel.description:
Well since my main (hashbrownie) got banned, I had to start a new account again. I don't know what kind of account I'm gonna make this one but it doesn't really matter.
Name: hymn of god(don't ask why) CB: 19
Stats: 20 hp 1 attack 26 strength 15 def 1 range 1 mage 21 prayer 30 wc 35 fm
Long-term Goals: 70 attack 80 strength 65 defence 60 range 50+ mage 52 prayer
Misc. Goals: 75 wc 99 fm 99 cooking 60 fishing 60 mining 70 smelting 60 rc
I hope to achieve all of these in the near future...
P.S. If anybody could give any donations, for skills like mage, prayer, and range, it would really help me out.
